{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give 2022/2023 GCSE students a choice between exams or teacher assessed grades",
        "additional_details": "Students in all years have suffered tremendously and have lacked over a year of education. Making them do GCSEs will not give them a proper chance to show their potential! Let them have a choice between doing their GCSEs or receiving predicted grades.",
        "background": "Let students who are currently in Year 9 and 10 have a choice when they come to do their GCSEs in 2022 and 2023, on whether they want teacher predicted grades or to take exams.",
